      "level": {
        "value": 11
      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> the darksphinx warden of the Vivified Labyrinth — brilliant, bitter, and bound. She knows all four rotations, pulls levers to split parties, and lairs at her throne (E20) with her surviving plaything: <strong>Vencarlo Orisini</strong>, chained at 0 HP.</p><p><strong>Tactics:</strong> scry, rotate, herd onto symbols, then pounce from darkness; she retreats by wand when bloodied and <strong>fights to the death</strong> within her prison. <strong>The lever she cannot pull:</strong> reveal Vimanda's treachery to her and the binding does the PCs' work.</p>",
      "publication": {
